-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/wafer-works-optr-august-sales-fall-82-19-table-5221-tt.html
WAFER WORKS OPTR said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 82.19% to NT$10,157,000 from NT$57,045,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales             10,157           57,045    
YOY%             -82.19%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            354,059          251,019    
YOY%              41.05% 
=================================================================
 